{"tid":1747334,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"敵人既敵人係邊個？點解奶美國個陣又咁識諗？","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T07:46:26.000Z","uid":58041,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0f672f23d0eb2727f64780eb4dc2395df707e1","tid":1747334,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"美國都唔係真心幫你，都係互相利用，但你地又識奶到足<br />\n又簽幾百個名又揮巨型美國旗<br />\n全因佢地係「敵人既敵人」，可以幫手制衡敵人<br />\n<br />\n但你地J完200萬人遊行<br />\n想搞流水式集會個陣就醒起搵泛民<br />\n搵律師，搵物資個陣就醒起搵泛民<br />\n人地今次都算落力幫<br />\n除非你想逼佢地呢個moment話支持武力革命除非你想佢地即時滅亡全部DQ晒俾建制奶晒你所有資源<br />\n唔該你地企係人地既角度諗下野<br />\n唔好諗到咩就逼人做咩好嗎？<br />\n然後你依家同我講唔射俾佢地要割佢地蓆？<br />\n你冇撚野下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係泛民告你暴動喎 唔係泛民害你打你喎<br />\n係建制班仆街同黑警呀<br />\n搞清楚未呀？醒未呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲有支持搞死cctvb個班，下年份sell bonus既約就12月先Deadline<br />\n你知唔知班幾球幾球咁簽既廣告商講咩？<br />\n人地話要等埋區選既結果再決定簽唔簽cctvb呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZo9qVY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZo9qVY.png&h=aad2e683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDD5JHE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDD5JHE.png&h=6d2956fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a88b781797ae7217ffbe85756ef9818a970c6ea7","tid":1747334,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db417cadaada43382d29cda81fdc06e82f0ee8e","tid":1747334,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af199fba664a77e301e803782bdcaeb3a5d4d39","tid":1747334,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"